```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='speakers')

ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'white' and {ANSWER1} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
